OL,4,Cperformance since revealing health
OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FCeline Dion has given her first live
OL,8,Fpublic performance since revealing she
OL,9,Fis living with stiff person syndrome
OL,10,F(SPS), at the opening ceremony of the
OL,11,FParis Olympics.
OL,13,FThe superstar closed the ceremony from
OL,14,Fthe Eiffel Tower, singing Edith Piaf's
OL,15,FL'Hymne A L'Amour (Hymn to Love).
OL,17,FHer appearance had been teased for
OL,18,Fweeks, but organisers and Dion's
OL,19,Frepresentatives had refused to confirm
OL,20,Fwhether she was performing.
