OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FThe Canadian singer cancelled her Las
OL,8,FVegas residency due to health concerns
OL,9,Fin 2021, before revealing her SPS
OL,10,Fdiagnosis in December 2022 and
OL,11,Fcancelling her Courage World Tour.
OL,13,FShe has not performed in public since.
OL,15,FShe wrote on Instagram: "I'm honoured
OL,16,Fto have performed tonight, for the
OL,17,FParis 2024 Opening Ceremony, and so
OL,18,Ffull of joy to be back in one of my
OL,19,Fvery favourite cities!
