OL,7,F"Most of all, I'm so happy to be
OL,8,Fcelebrating these amazing athletes,
OL,9,Fwith all their stories of sacrifice
OL,10,Fand determination, pain and
OL,11,Fperseverance.
OL,13,F"All of you have been so focused on
OL,14,Fyour dream, and whether or not you
OL,15,Ftake home a medal, I hope that being
OL,16,Fhere means that it has come true for
OL,17,Fyou!
