OL,7,F"You should all be so proud, we know
OL,8,Fhow hard you have worked to be the
OL,9,Fbest of the best. Stay focused, keep
OL,10,Fgoing, my heart is with you!"
OL,12,FShe appeared in the final moments of
OL,13,Fthe Olympics pageantry dressed in a
OL,14,Fbeaded silver gown with a high
OL,15,Fneckline and appeared emotional as she
OL,16,Fcame to the climax of the song.
OL,18,FDion's rare condition causes
OL,19,Fprogressive muscular inflexibility.
