OL,5,Ccondition
OL,7,FHer struggles are documented in her
OL,8,F2024 documentary I Am: Celine Dion, in
OL,9,Fwhich she spoke about her desire to
OL,10,Freturn to performing.
OL,12,FIn June, at the premiere of the
OL,13,Fdocumentary, she said that returning
OL,14,Frequired therapy, "physically,
OL,15,Fmentally, emotionally, vocally".
OL,17,FShe added: "So that's why it takes a
OL,18,Fwhile. But absolutely why we're doing
OL,19,Fthis because I'm already a little bit
OL,20,Fback."
